The evidence with the title 'Obamacare replacement could save $2 trillion over two decades ... ' says Mar 23, 2017  ... While CBO has n't yet provided second decade estimates (other than to say the bill would not be deficit - increasing ) , we estimate – very roughly – that the bill would save $ 2 trillion over two decades , including $ 1.6 trillion between 2027and2036.Including interest, we estimate 20-year savings of $2.4 trillion. 
